39. (Dependency by head: i den förfluten analyzing relative distance not the last dependence, since end is nil)
 Dependency distance: N/A (there is a period, it is nil as head, above would not count)

Average dependency distance calculation:

Now summing all of the non-nil, non-N/A distances for all words and get the total of 69. The total words with a definite dependency relationship are 39.
To get the average, we calculate the sum (69) and divide by the total (39) -> 69/39 = 1.769.